caption: The Browse modal's transform picker
tags: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/tokens
title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/tokens/browse-picker
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The Browse modal — opened from any binding row in the editor — has an
//Optional transform// dropdown listing every registered transform.  Picking
one tells the click-to-fill action to insert `{{path|name}}` instead of
`{{path}}`.  Built-ins and user-defined transforms appear in the same list.
